{"tid":782893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學研究：男人50歲時最吸引 女性18歲時最搶手","createTime":"2018-08-17T06:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T01:14:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"cd3b4e87a3475dba9e720a966016bed06c8a155a","tid":782893,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.cc/gczetpe41/Bikini_Girl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.cc%2Fgczetpe41%2FBikini_Girl.jpg&h=154f8900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《先端科學》（Science Advances）發表一篇新研究，調查網上約會平台的用戶，顯示50歲男性最富魅力；而女性在18歲時最搶手，之後人氣逐漸下滑，且教育程度越高，對異性吸引力越低。兩性尋覓對象的觀點大不同，出現「老少配」也無需意外。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員從免費網上約會平台取樣，計算用戶一個月內收到的訊息量。近20萬位異性戀用戶之中，50歲男性最受女性歡迎，18歲女性最受男性關注；女性18歲過後，在異性眼中吸引力逐步下降，而教育程度越高，對男性吸引力可能降低。男性則相反，所受教育越多，在女性看來更有魅力。<br />\n<br />\n這個研究結果，與知名網上約會網站OkCupid在2010年分享的數據相符。OkCupid當時發現，幾乎所有22歲至30歲男性，都對年紀比他們小的女性比較有興趣；多數男性會尋找相對年輕的女性，上限是和自己相近的歲數，較難接受年長太多女性。<br />\n<br />\n專門探討科技與人際的心理學家Michelle Drouin博士對研究結果不感訝異，她表示，這符合生物交配的進化論，「年輕」象徵了「生育力」，事關繁衍。此外，女性的高等教育程度，會被轉化「事業心較強」、「重心不在感情或家庭」的意味。另外，目前還有理論認為，男性在擇偶時更重視肉體魅力，較不注重配偶的收入或權勢。<br />\n<br />\n必須注意的是，網上約會平台反映出人們內心渴望，但不一定是現實生活中想要或需要的。這項研究其中一個重點發現是，大多數用戶發送訊息的對象，幾乎都是比自身條件更好、更具吸引力，這往往和現實狀況不太一樣。畢竟影響感情變化的因素有很多，共同興趣或特殊專長，也可能帶來特別的化學反應。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》"},{"pid":"3b569f0fc43719f78c19861128b181db50a1fbc8","tid":782893,"uid":31215,"like":154,"dislike":5,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"又做無聊研究講埋啲阿媽係女人，人人都知嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心理學都係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4f7f1124b5757508f6f14af7a153c37f13a32a","tid":782893,"uid":153778,"like":60,"dislike":18,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"成班契弟唔識食，女人一定係三十到尾最有女人味最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佐佐木明希<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7281e7e8c926205a788bf01206f1e12129489411","tid":782893,"uid":31215,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"quote":{"pid":"9f4f7f1124b5757508f6f14af7a153c37f13a32a","tid":782893,"uid":153778,"like":60,"dislike":18,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"成班契弟唔識食，女人一定係三十到尾最有女人味最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佐佐木明希<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:45:31.000Z","msg":"唐姨岩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5536d5d0816d23024ada70d6c336f8ec6ef556","tid":782893,"uid":53687,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:49:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾研究，男人梗係以財富做指標"},{"pid":"1177aa92dc5c0f960518a2061c6f45fb303394f6","tid":782893,"uid":29702,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a1bb20d7d702c25c12f6521d3be45518c194b4c","tid":782893,"uid":29702,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:51:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89abd28c2c3f4ce8860a54089c49aa29c80d7538","tid":782893,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"1177aa92dc5c0f960518a2061c6f45fb303394f6","tid":782893,"uid":29702,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score